洋人主子，獻財獻子女，為博得西方自由國度的一條後路，今日盡搜刮香港人的血汗民脂民膏，他日盡帶其金銀財寶，享西方自由國度<br />\n<br />\n世人看在眼裏，鬼佬看在眼裏，<br />\n此等無恥之徒，沐猴而冠，比不上耍戲之馬騮<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n妄自尊大衝昏頭腦，享其榮華名聲，縱之以淫慾<br />\n<br />\n言教遠不及其所行為之身教，一旦其暗裏所作為之事違其所言教，即使千言萬言予以人&quot;&quot;教化&quot;&quot;，實必不攻自破，今世人得以明察，此等人過往冠冕堂皇之幻象，如今卻五經掃地，實在是對眾人耳目同智商，及上天神靈之大褻瀆!<br />\n<br />\n有良知，明見的人，何以不憤恨?  何以不悲當今之上樑不正，禮崩樂壞?"},{"pid":"a5094f5ba0e7c42392bf8aad1da467481667ff27","tid":2019243,"uid":47901,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T06:55:47.000Z","msg":"英國呀，英國呀!  <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62e737f0bd2ec4941cfb468b374dc7371a5439be","tid":2019243,"uid":123774,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"quote":{"pid":"c302b273d1a9ea87fd230c6895860b925775cb29","tid":2019243,"uid":53003,"like":50,"dislike":1,"score":49,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T06:54:09.000Z","msg":"英國讀書，漢奸"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T06:56:18.000Z","msg":"班高官仔女好似都幾福薄<br />\n<br />\n梁振英生咗個癲嘅女<br />\n張華峰死左個癲嘅女"},{"pid":"dab605091ad41318dfb19ec782301def73c203e0","tid":2019243,"uid":204750,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68aaa429c2e45cd766e4ffc35a45bceab3109bc0","tid":2019243,"uid":25900,"like":55,"dislike":1,"score":54,"citedBy":1,"replyTi