金銀財寶，享西方自由國度<br />\n<br />\n世人看在眼裏，鬼佬看在眼裏，<br />\n此等無恥之徒，沐猴而冠，比不上耍戲之馬騮<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n妄自尊大衝昏頭腦，享其榮華名聲，縱之以淫慾<br />\n<br />\n言教遠不及其所行為之身教，一旦其暗裏所作為之事違其所言教，即使千言萬言予以人&quot;&quot;教化&quot;&quot;，實必不攻自破，今世人得以明察，此等人過往冠冕堂皇之幻象，如今卻五經掃地，實在是對眾人耳目同智商，及上天神靈之大褻瀆!<br />\n<br />\n有良知，明見的人，何以不憤恨?  何以不悲當今之上樑不正，禮崩樂壞?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T23:23:41.000Z","msg":"先生之話正說中我肺腑之言<br />\n今國之大亂全因班賣港狗賊<br />\n借愛國名義實施暴政<br />\n他日名成利就則到外國定居<br />\n懶理暴政下百姓生死<br />\n於西方世界樂不思蜀<br />\n願此等奸賊必受天誅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6383cb08dccce7f76c22da578c4b6e3481acc22d","tid":2019243,"uid":222907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T23:38:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kEnMOPa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkEnMOPa.jpg&h=ebe47424&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"25754de353ea29f73ad67242765dc0cc916e5a9f","tid":2019243,"uid":165442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fed02623e80a1d80cd4040d40dd85cea18623b24","tid":2019243,"uid":126508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T11:41:17.000Z","msg":"林鄭做奶奶的每日生活係點過？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T23:46:40.000Z","msg":"同老公講<br />\n你日日比人屌老母"},{"pid":"4d7e9221aae72d1d403385c065bdb923a2c98368","tid":2019243,"uid":47901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6383cb08dccce7f76c22da578c4b6e3481acc22d","tid":2019243,"uid":222907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T23:38:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kEnMOPa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkEnMOPa.jpg&h=ebe47424&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T00:15:38.000Z","msg":"佢老味丫........<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkg